Commentary: Shami to Bairstow, 3 runs, dropped! Great effort from KL at mid-off but these need to stick if KXIP are to make a comeback. Dived full-length to his right and also got his right hand to it but it didn't stick. Parried it all the way towards the deep before it was hauled back in. Bairstow is living dangerously here, stepped down for the flat-batted hit, didn't keep it down and would be happy that it didn't go to hand
